metadata.name: LOSS
metadata.description:
Sometimes we win, sometimes we lose. Loss is a part of life, and we should learn from it and move forward stronger and smarter each day.

Thank you to Justin Trimble for the use of his Chromie Squiggles, to XCOPY for the arm, and to Kevin Rose as the inspiration for this piece, from his loss of 25 Chromie Squiggles.
